    "UIName": "Scribe",
    "Id": "chassisdef_scribe_SCR-800",
    "Name": "Scribe",
    "Details": "The Scribe SCR-800 is a 45-ton Draconis Combine medium BattleMech produced by Blankenburg Technologies in 3066 as a fast, well-armored generalist design. A left-arm ER PPC provides long-range hitting power, while a right-torso MML 3 fed by separate LRM and SRM ammunition bins extends the engagement envelope in both directions. A right-arm Sword serves as a capable melee weapon for close-quarters combat. Five jump jets and Ferro-Fibrous armor round out a highly mobile and resilient package.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Accurate Weapon - PPC</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.03</color></b>",
    "Icon": "uixTxrIcon_scribe"
  },
  "VariantName": "SCR-800",
