  "StockRole": "Skirmisher",
  "YangsThoughts": "The Scribe came out of a rushed DCMS development program in the mid-3060s and ended up serving all the way through the Jihad and into Republic of the Sphere service, which is a solid track record for what was essentially a quick-turnaround contract job. The ER PPC gives it genuine reach for a 45-ton machine, and the Sword is a real threat to anything that closes thinking it has an easy target. Not a complicated mech, but it does what it was designed to do without much fuss.",
